If the user has left some text in the quicksearch field, then clicking any link will bring up a message box asking the following question:

{quote}
_Are you sure you want to navigate away from this page?_

_You have entered new data on this page. If you navigate away from this page without first saving your data, the changes will be lost._

_Press OK to continue, or Cancel to stay on the current page._
{quote}

RSS Feeds not authenticating correctly.

{quote}
Jonathan Nolen: so, ever since 2.4 got released to StAC, none of my Streams RSS feeds will authenticate
{quote}

During the report of the bug to me, Jonathan said that he had trouble with a normal login, he could not log in at all for about five minutes.  This may be related to the RSS issue, we should check the logs.
